description: Lists all datasets currently available in your account, filtering on the dataset name.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: An opaque pagination token indicating where to continue the listing of datasets.

nested_items.name: DatasetSummaries
nested_items.description: Provides information about the specified dataset, including creation time, dataset ARN, and status.

nested_items.name: DatasetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the specified dataset.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: Indicates the status of the dataset.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
